1213
01:28:00,347 --> 01:28:03,507
Like my dad used to say, carpe diem.

1214
01:28:03,607 --> 01:28:06,243
Let's boff and be merry?

1215
01:28:08,555 --> 01:28:11,072
- Okay.
- Great.

1216
01:28:11,172 --> 01:28:14,442
Great. And... one last thing.

1217
01:28:14,880 --> 01:28:18,282
- Can I take a shower, please?
- He really stinks.

1218
01:28:19,655 --> 01:28:24,877
Thank you, everybody, for coming.
I would like to thank my agent,

1219
01:28:24,977 --> 01:28:26,542
Tim Prince.

1220
