- Just give me a minute, all right?

1235
01:30:08,563 --> 01:30:10,259
Okay.

1236
01:30:20,430 --> 01:30:22,184
Hi.

1237
01:30:23,488 --> 01:30:27,534
- You came.
- I came. Piece of cake.

1238
01:30:31,213 --> 01:30:33,709
I came because I love you.

1239
01:30:35,130 --> 01:30:37,525
I came because I need you.

1240
01:30:38,921 --> 01:30:41,171
I need my son.

1241
01:30:41,271 --> 01:30:43,555
I need my family.

1242
01:30:43,655 --> 01:30:45,709
That's why I came.

1243
01:30:47,921 --> 01:30:51,246
